author: Cindy Chasteen
title: Cindy Chasteen
text: I got a Quote: from 3 local shops for simple mattes cut for 2 matching pictures, NOTHING fancy at all. They were all so ridiculously high, I could even see the embarrassment on the associate's face. None compared to the quality, price or turnaround time that I was promised and received from American Frame. I have a new GO-TO framing supplier! THANK YOU AMERICAN FRAME!
